name: Examining Health Data from a Dorm
tagline: MSBA 6320 Spring 2016: Eric Weber, Christina Engstrom and Joe Ellis
body:
This repository contains the materials for the MSBA 6320 Group Project from Spring 2016.

Below are the links to the html and pdf files of the final report.

[HTML Version of Report](Final_Report_Markdown.html)

[PDF Version of Report](Final_Report_Markdown.pdf)

Click through to the github repository for specific files, or download everything in the zip file above.

You can contact us about the project at edweber at umn dot edu. 

Thanks,

Eric, Christina and Joe
